  Source:
    Title: Harijan
    Editor: Mohandas Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 24 April 1937
---
WHatever you do, be true to yourselves and to the world. Hide not your
thoughts. If it is shameful to reveal them, it is more shameful to think
them.
